1. Informatica Intelligent Cloud Services(IICS) is an integration platform as a service (iPaas)
2. It has multiple services underneath - Data Quality, Data Integration, Data Profiling etc

Data Integration Service can be used to build and run advanced, complex integrations using pre-built functions and templates for mappings and transformations

--IDMC Architecture
  1. Informatica cloud
  2. Secure agent
  3. Informatica Cloud DWH

- What is informatica secure Agent
  Informatica secure agent runs all the tasks and establishes the communication between informatica cloud services and your organization and helps in transfers
  data between source and target.
